[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年大西洋飓风季]]是继1851年开始有纪录以来最活跃的[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风季]]之一，形成了19场获得命名的[[风暴|风暴]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Extremely Active Atlantic Hurricane Season was a 'Gentle Giant' for U.S. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102194739/http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2010/20101129_hurricaneseason.html | url = http://www.noaanews.noaa.gov/stories2010/20101129_hurricaneseason.html | work = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2010-11-29 | accessdate = 2014-09-03 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|根据[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]的定义，一个大西洋飓风季平均会形成12场热带风暴，其中6个会成为飓风，两场会达到大型飓风强度<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-06-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140606234002/http://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/outlooks/background_information.shtml#NOAADEF | url = http://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/outlooks/background_information.shtml#NOAADEF | title = Background Information: The North Atlantic Hurricane Season | publisher = Climate Prediction Center | author = Climate Prediction Center Internet Team | accessdate = 2014-06-25 | date = 2011-08-04 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。飓风季从2010年6月1日正式开始，同年11月30日结束，传统上这样的日期界定了一年中绝大多数[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]形成和发展的时间段<ref name="SeasonDates">{{cite book | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601034216/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html | title = Hurricane Research Division: Frequently Asked Questions | chapter = G: Tropical Cyclone Climatology | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | chapterurl = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqG.html | at = [http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html G1) When is hurricane season ?] | author1 = Chris Landsea | author2 = Neal Dorst (ed.) | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 2011-06-02 | accessdate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>。6月25日形成的[[2010年飓风亚历克斯|飓风亚历克斯]]是全季首场[[风暴|风暴]]，最后一场风暴[[飓风托马斯|飓风托马斯]]则在11月7日消散。

全季一共产生了21个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中19个达到[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]强度，12场成为飓风，5场达到大型飓风标准{{#tag:ref|大型飓风是指[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]可以在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中达到三级或以上的风暴<ref>{{cite book | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | title = Hurricane Research Division: Frequently Asked Questions | chapter = A: Basic Definitions | chapterurl = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqA.html | archivedate = 2014-04-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140426044722/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html | deadurl = no | at = [http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A3.html A3) What is a super-typhoon? What is a major hurricane ? What is an intense hurricane ?] | author1 = Chris Landsea | author2 = Neal Dorst (ed.) | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 2011-06-02 | accessdate = 2014-06-25 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。本季造成损失和人员伤亡最多的两场飓风分别是[[飓风伊戈尔|伊戈尔]]和托马斯，其中伊戈尔[[风眼|中心]]向外风力达到[[烈风|烈风]]强度的范围直径创下新纪录，其[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]一度达到每小时250公里，属[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|四级飓风]]标准，数天后再以一级飓风强度袭击[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Pasch, Richard J | author2 = Kimberlain, Todd B | author3 = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-02-15 | accessdate = 2014-09-03 | type = Tropical Cyclone Report | title = Hurricane Igor | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130612063408/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL112010_Igor.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL112010_Igor.pdf | pages = 1–20 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | archivedate = 2013-06-12 }}</ref>。托马斯的形成日期较晚，在进入东[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]后迅速强化，达到风力时速160公里强度。虽然这一天气系统并未[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但仍对[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]构成严重影响，之后还以热带风暴强度冲击了[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东南部<ref>{{cite report | author = Pasch, Richard J | author2 = Kimberlain, Todd B | author3 = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-03-07 | accessdate = 2014-09-03 | type = Tropical Cyclone Report | pages = 1–20 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | title = Hurricane Tomas | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140408220223/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL212010_Tomas.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL212010_Tomas.pdf | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | archivedate = 2014-04-08 }}</ref>。

'''2010年大西洋飓风季时间轴'''中记录了全年大西洋所有热带或[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]形成、增强、减弱、登陆、[[温带气旋|转变成温带气旋]]以及消散的具体信息。还包括实际操作中没有发布的信息，如[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]在风暴过后进行的回顾。包括最大持续风速、位置、距离在内的所有数字都是经四舍五入换算成整数<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ | title = 2010 Tropical Cyclone Advisory Archive | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-02-07 | accessdate = 2014-09-03 | type = Archive | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140220115231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-02-20 }}</ref>。

